  "summary": "Binary columnar storage with sort keys for zone maps. Lineitem sorted by l_shipdate (critical for Q1/Q6 block skipping). Orders sorted by o_orderdate, customer/part/supplier by primary keys. Dictionary encoding for low-cardinality strings (l_returnflag, l_linestatus, c_mktsegment, o_orderstatus, o_orderpriority, l_shipinstruct, l_shipmode). Zone maps on lineitem date/discount/quantity filters. Hash indexes for join keys (c_custkey→o_custkey, o_orderkey→l_orderkey). DECIMAL columns stored as int64_t scaled by 100 to avoid IEEE 754 precision errors."
